<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Day Vy Cosmetics - Product Promotion</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #222222;
      }

      a {
        color:#fff;
        text-decoration:none;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 30px;
        color: #f086d9;
        text-align: center;
      }

        .email-body {
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #f4f3f3;
            min-height: 70vh;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 14px;
            color: #d55fbb;
            text-align: center;
        }

        img {
			padding: 24px;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .product-list {
			display: flex;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			justify-content: space-around;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .product-item {
            background-color: #fff;
			border: 1px solid #ccc;
			padding: 15px;
			width: 45%;
			box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			text-align: center;
        }

        .product-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
			margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .product-item h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
			margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .product-item p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
			color: #555;
        }

        .product-item a {
            background-color: #d55fbb;
            color: #555;
			padding: 10px 20px;
			border-radius: 5px;
        }
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="email-wrapper">
		<div class="email-header">
      <img src="https://i.ibb.co/4W8m0wz/logo.png" style="height:200px; width:200px;" alt="Day Vy Cosmetics Logo"/>
	  </div>
	  <div class="email-body">
    <p>Dear Valued Customer,</p>
    <p>
      We hope this message finds you well! At Day Vy Cosmetics, we are always striving to bring you the best in beauty and self-care. As a token of our appreciation for your continued support, we are thrilled to announce a special promotion just for you.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Enjoy exclusive discounts on our latest products!</strong> Whether you're looking to refresh your skincare routine or try something new, now is the perfect time to treat yourself.
    </p>
    <p>
      <ul>
        <li>Up to 30% off selected items</li>
        <li>Free shipping on orders over $50</li>
        <li>Special gifts with every purchase</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
      Visit our website to explore these amazing deals. Hurry, the offer is valid for a limited time only!
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for being a part of the Day Vy Cosmetics. We look forward to helping you shine!
    </p>
    <p>
      With love,<br/>
      The Day Vy Cosmetics Team
    </p>
	<div class="product-list">
	  <% products.forEach(product => { %>
		<div class="product-item">
		  <img src="<%= product.image %>" alt="<%= product.name %>"/>
		  <h3><%= product.name %></h3>
		  <p><%= product.description %></p>
		  <a href="<%= product.link %>">Shop Now</a>
		</div>
	  <% }); %>
	</div>

	<p>
		Enjoy shopping with exclusive offer, beauty tips and discover your favourite products. Thank you for being a part of Day Vy Cosmetics!
	</p>
  </div>
  <div class="email-footer">
	&copy;2025 Day Vy Cosmetics. All rights reserved.
  </div>
  </div>
	</body>
</html>
